 SABC Sport has accepted his decision to repudiate his contract with the SABC which he entered into with SABC Sport on the 6th of June 2017. The SABC engaged Mr. Marawa several times to try and remedy the situation the broadcaster said in a statement.Sully Motsweni Group Executive of Sport paid tribute to him.She said: Mr. Marawa contributed immensely to the Sport brand within the organisation especially on radio station Metro FM. It was hard for us to accept but we concede to his decision . The SABC also thanked Marawa for his service to SABC Sport and Radio at large. The corporation wishes him well in his future endeavours. 